# Requirements

   - python > 2.7
   - mail-server

Start mmailer with --help to find out how to use it!

   $ sh mmailer.py --help

* be aware that mmailer saves your password in cleartext right now in the config file.

look under samples for the format a mail.txt file should have:

 > ./tests/samples/mail.txt

For each mail you want to send, fill out one line of substitude in the csv file.


Have fun!


